OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784542749
OL,3,CMan dies after getting into difficulty
OL,4,Cin the sea
OL,6,FPolice have confirmed a man has died
OL,7,Fafter getting into difficulty in the
OL,8,Fsea near Cullercoats Bay in North
OL,9,FTyneside.
OL,11,FOfficers were alerted by the ambulance
OL,12,Fservice over concerns for the welfare
OL,13,Fof two men who were in the water.
OL,15,FEmergency services were deployed, and
OL,16,Fboth men were recovered from the water.
OL,18,FOne of the men, aged in his 20s, was
OL,19,Fpronounced dead at the scene, police
OL,20,Fhave said.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/3
