OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784542749
OL,3,CMan dies after getting into difficulty
OL,4,Cin the sea
OL,6,FThe other man, also aged in his 20s,
OL,7,Fwas taken to hospital where he remains
OL,8,Fin a serious but stable condition.
OL,10,FThe next of kin of both men have been
OL,11,Fcontacted and are being supported by
OL,12,Fofficers.
OL,14,FChief Inspector Simon Wotton, of
OL,15,FNorthumbria Police, said: "This is an
OL,16,Fabsolutely tragic incident and the
OL,17,Fthoughts of everyone here at
OL,18,FNorthumbria Police are with anyone
OL,19,Faffected by this incident.
OL,26,@wD@[OU
