PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784542749
OL,3,CMan dies after getting into difficulty
OL,4,Cin the sea
OL,6,F"We'd like to thank our partner
OL,7,Fagencies who were there working
OL,8,Falongside police last night, and I am
OL,9,Fsure they are just as saddened by this
OL,10,Foutcome as we are.
OL,12,F"We know this will be a greatly
OL,13,Fshocking and distressing incident for
OL,14,Fthose involved and for the local
OL,15,Fcommunity, but we'd ask the public to
OL,16,Frespect the privacy of anyone who may
OL,17,Fhave been affected."
OL,19,FA report has been made to the coroner.
